{"tid":1508690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"HA：醫護人員幫示威者通知家屬 可能要負上刑事責任","createTime":"2019-08-26T14:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T23:03:13.000Z","uid":75557,"like":10,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"18313501225a18ea1bcc891692e3990a57f0269a","tid":1508690,"uid":75557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:57:48.000Z","msg":"有識人係某間醫院做緊 高層岀咗內部文件要求醫護人員<br />\n1. 醫護人員幫被拘捕示威者通知其家屬時，需得警犬同意 如果唔係就有可能要負上刑事責任<br />\n2. 如有臨床需要，醫護人員需得警犬approve，先可以聯絡家屬<br />\n想講警犬憑咩咁樣干涉醫護人員嘅正常工作程序，入院就要通知家屬，戲都係咁做啦<br />\n依家擺明警權過大，恐嚇醫護人員<br />\n要推到全世界都知佢哋嘅惡行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LY2EPVw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLY2EPVw.png&h=8cb4dc88&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a75c1e25ff26480e9e2e592a821d4ea53e82cee","tid":1508690,"uid":57629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:00:26.000Z","msg":"乜啲狗權力大到咁？<br />\n推爆佢！！！！"},{"pid":"02d492438e92e02574776c5e2dae8049f8f52223","tid":1508690,"uid":75557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T15:00:46.000Z","msg":"HA secret 都有人開post 有詳細啲嘅版本<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2303923496396358&amp;id=731331330322257\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2303923496396358%26id%3D731331330322257&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=7cef8975\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2303923496396358&amp;id=731331330322257</a>"},{"pid":"f3381ad37457db5269edae50d298ad15d63feac0","tid":1508690,"uid":2734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep